    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cement produced by taking finely pulverizing calcined argillaceous limestone and heating it to complete decarbonation, which is the process of removing carbon dioxide.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
